name: Fortunes
tagline: fortunes - fortunes files for the TV shows Firefly and Community. Has a script to email you a fortune every day.
body:
### get your fortune.
Every day get an email with an assortment of fortunes from Community, Star Trek, Firefly, Parks and Rec, Star Wars, Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy and more!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
